	<h2><p> Difference Between Order and UnOrder list </h2></p>
	<h4><p> <b> Order List:</h4></b></p>
	<p><em> <u>Syntax of Order List:</u></em></p>
	<p>< ol > <br>
	 < li >< /li > <br>
	 -<br>
	 -<br>
	 <p>< /ol ></p>
	<h2><p> Wroking of Order List Tags.</h2></p>
	<p><b> In Numbering sequence , like 1,2,3....:</b> </p>
	<ol>
	<li>KPR</li>
	<li>KPK</li>
	<li>RYK</li>
	<li>JDW</li>
	</ol>
	
	<h2><p> In small alphabets , like a,b,c....:</h2></p>
	<ol type="a">
	<li>model town</li>
	<li>jinnah town</li>
	<li>riaz town</li>
	<li>jaddah town</li>
	</ol>
	
	<h2><p> In Capital Alphabets , like A,B,C....:</h2></p>
	<ol type="A">
	<li>MODEL TOWN</li>
	<li>JINNAH TOWN</li>
	<li>RIAZ TOWN</li>
	<li>JADDAH TOWN</li>
	</ol>
	
	<h2><p> In small roman , like i,ii,iii,....:</h2></p>
	<ol type="i">
	<li>model town</li>
	<li>model town</li>
	<li>model town</li>
	<li>model town</li>
	</ol>
	<h2><p> In Capital Alphabets , like I,II,III,....:</h2></p>
	<ol type="I">
	<li>MODEL TOWN</li>
	<li>JINNAH TOWN</li>
	<li>RIAZ TOWN</li>
	<li>JADDAH TOWN</li>
	</ol>
	<h4><p> <b> UnOrder List:</h4></b></p>
	<p><em> <u>Syntax of UnOrder List:</u></em></p>
	<p>< ul > <br>
	 < li >< /li > <br>
	 -<br>
	 -<br>
	 <p>< /ul ></p>
	 <h2><p> Wroking of UnOrder List Tags.</h2></p>
	<p><b> In default(disk):</b> </p>
	<ul>
	<li>KPR</li>
	<li>KPK</li>
	<li>RYK</li>
	<li>JDW</li>
	</ul>
	 
	<p><b> In Square :</b> </p>
	<ul type="square">
	<li>KPR</li>
	<li>KPK</li>
	<li>RYK</li>
	<li>JDW</li>
	</ul>
	
	<p><b> In Circle:</b> </p>
	<ul type="circle">
	<li>KPR</li>
	<li>KPK</li>
	<li>RYK</li>
	<li>JDW</li>
	</ul>
